userDescription: I am a Full Stack Software Engineer with 5 years of experience in developing scalable web applications. I hold a Bachelor's degree in Computer Science from Stanford University, graduated in 2019 with a GPA of 3.8. I have worked at Google as a Senior Software Engineer from 2021 to present, where I led the development of a microservices architecture that improved system performance by 40%. Previously, I worked at Amazon as a Software Developer from 2019 to 2021, building cloud-based solutions using AWS and Java Spring Boot. My technical skills include Java, Python, JavaScript, React, Node.js, Spring Boot, Docker, Kubernetes, AWS, and MySQL. I have completed several notable projects including an E-commerce Platform using React and Node.js that handles 10,000+ daily transactions, and a Real-time Chat Application built with WebSocket and Redis for instant messaging. I am passionate about clean code, system design, and continuous learning.
